  world: "Generic"
  description: "This spell functions like summon nature\'s ally I, except that you can summon one 8th-level creature, 1d3 7th-level creatures of the same kind, or 1d4+1 lower-level creatures of the same kind.  When you use a summoning spell to summon an air, chaotic, earth, evil, fire, good, lawful, or water creature, it is a spell of that type."
  short_description: "Calls creature to fight."
}
